name: Coyote Canyon
description:
Introduction

Coyote Canyon is a beautiful 4x4 trail in the north of Anza-Borrego Desert State Park.

Approach

Take Di Gorgio Road to get there. Signage and Google directions are terrible.

Descent

Exit

Red tape

This road can be in easy or high clearance conditions. Check before you visit.
